---
const studentFemale = "/student_female_learning_1778817112740.png";
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-[#F8FAFC] relative overflow-hidden border-t border-slate-100">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="relative bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-[3.5rem] p-12 md:p-20 lg:p-24 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/40">
      
      <!-- Glowing Decorative Orbs (Soft Light Accent) -->
      <div class="absolute -top-40 -left-40 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[#6320EE]/5 blur-[130px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -right-40 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[#C6F432]/8 blur-[140px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
      
      <!-- Decorative Grid Pattern -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,rgba(99,32,238,0.02)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,rgba(99,32,238,0.02)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:3rem_3rem] pointer-events-none"></div>

      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16 relative z-10">
        
        <!-- Text Content -->
        <div class="flex-1 text-center lg:text-left space-y-8">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-[#6320EE]/10 border border-[#6320EE]/20 text-[#6320EE] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
            <span>✨</span> Komunitas LENTERA
          </span>
          
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-slate-900 leading-tight">
            Untuk Fitur yang Lebih Lengkap <br />
            <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#6320EE] to-[#8C52FF]">
              dan berinteraksi dengan sesama pengguna!
            </span>
          </h2>
          
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-base md:text-lg max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
            Dapatkan akses ke materi eksklusif, webinar bersama pakar pendidikan, dan diskusi seru bersama ribuan siswa lainnya di seluruh Indonesia.
          </p>
          
          <div class="pt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4">
            <a href="#start" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-[#C6F432] hover:bg-[#b3dd2d] text-slate-950 font-black text-lg px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl transition-all shadow-xl shadow-[#C6F432]/20 hover:shadow-[#C6F432]/40 active:scale-95">
              Daftar Sekarang
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
              </svg>
            </a>
            
            <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-600 hover:text-[#6320EE] font-bold text-base px-6 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-[#6320EE]/5 transition-all">
              Pelajari Benefit <span>📖</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Image & Decorative Elements -->
        <div class="flex-1 hidden lg:block relative">
          <!-- Main Image Frame with slight rotation -->
          <div class="relative z-10 rotate-[2deg] hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out group">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-amber-400 to-[#C6F432] rounded-[3.5rem] -rotate-[4deg] scale-[1.02] opacity-25 blur-sm"></div>
            
            <!-- White Border Container -->
            <div class="relative bg-white p-3 rounded-[3.5rem] border-2 border-slate-100 shadow-2xl">
              <img 
                src={studentFemale} 
                alt="Community" 
                class="w-[420px] h-[420px] object-cover rounded-[2.8rem]" 
              />
            </div>
            
            <!-- Floating Badge 1: Members Count -->
            <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-10 bg-white border border-slate-100 p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-xl flex items-center gap-3 animate-bounce [animation-duration:3s]">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#6320EE]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-lg">👥</div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Bergabung</p>
                <p class="text-slate-900 font-black text-sm">10k+ Anggota</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Floating Badge 2: Live status -->
            <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-white border border-slate-100 p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-xl flex items-center gap-3 animate-pulse">
              <div class="relative w-3 h-3 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full">
                <span class="absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-emerald-400 opacity-75 animate-ping"></span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Diskusi Live</p>
                <p class="text-slate-900 font-black text-sm">24/7 Aktif</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

